divs: Sighting DetailsHad a party for a wedding and a ufo showed up over 20 saw it less than a 100 yards in the back yard tree top level clear sky no clouds no moon but it light up the back yard like day time and created a cloud cover in shrewsbury off of lake street near route 20 and i got a call that it was also seen in lecester,ma also that night 1hr before and it didnt move.
Summary: still high power white beam of light tree top level straight to the ground no sound
